long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
By this extension, you can get a virtual phone number in just a couple of seconds!

SMS-MAN extension was created to improve the quality of service for people who are interested in both one-time and mass activation of accounts of various payment services and social networks that require confirmation by sending a SMS to a mobile number.

## What Information, You will get from this Extension ## 

1. Sms-man offers to receive SMS to a virtual phone number for signing up for more than 500 popular services on the most beneficial terms.

2. You will get SMS instantly at any time of the day or night.

3. Helps to Get The virtual phone number rent service information's allows you to receive an infinite amount of SMS during the period you paid for.

4. Virtual phone numbers for getting SMS from more than 270 countries are always available.
